                     <interp inst="t18280703-21-person234" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am clerk at the Post-office at Bristol. On the 18th of February, I tied and sealed the Hounslow bag - it laid on the board with other bags for the guard.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280703-21-person235">
                  MARY 
                  WHITE
               <interp inst="t18280703-21-person235" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
