                     <interp inst="t18280703-21-person235" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . My father is Post-master of Reading. On the 18th of February I put the letters into the Hounslow bag, tied and sealed it, and delivered it to William Cook, who exchanges the bags.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280703-21-person236">
                  WILLIAM 
                  COOK
               <interp inst="t18280703-21-person236" type="surname" value="COOK"></interp>
